    "created_at": "2015-07-21T18:40:49Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-07-21T18:40:49Z",
    "body": "> The Windows Github app which is a regular desktop app, displays dialogs that use the new style. Is it possible to get Electron to use the same?\n\nGitHub for Windows implements this 100% custom, there's no built-in API to do this in Windows. However, you could implement this super easily using the `<dialog>` tag. \n"
